  Goal: confirm whether 1777458629 / 1777458630 (and the few above them) are new
   from this boot, and what filename / type they actually are (dmesg-erst,
  dmesg-efi, or something else). If any new dmesg.txt exists, paste it.

  If no new pstore entry was written for this hang, that's the diagnostic answer
   — and it changes the model. panic_on_warn=1 + slub_debug=FZP should produce
