● Done. Summary of changes:

  Diagnosis upgraded: Confirmed write-after-free on skbuff_small_head (the
  slab_nomerge unmasked the real cache — round 1's skbuff_head_cache was a
  merged alias). 16 bytes of pointer-shaped garbage written into a freed object
  body, redzones intact. panic_on_warn=1 worked perfectly — the panic flushed to
   pstore in 20 EFI variable slots. The crash hit without an s2idle cycle, which
